Written by EBMUD: Prepared by RMC as part of work on EBMUD’s 2012 Revised Final Flow Modeling and Limits Report. Delineates what land area contributes to which parts of the EBMUD Interceptor.

  • ITAID – Unique identifier/ITA name

  • INTID – EBMUD interceptor Asset ID

  • Comment – general comments. Mostly just indicates if an ITA was not monitored as part of the 2009-10 ITA baseline flow monitoring study.

  • MID – Gives sub-ITA names. Only differs from ITAID when multiple sub-ITAs were grouped for flow metering quantification purposes.

attrdomv.udom: Sequential unique whole numbers that are automatically generated.
